content:
endobson opened issue #6679:

The link from cli to cli-logging is broken on docs.wasmtime.dev. The link works fine on the github repo, but in the html rendered documentation it 404s.

Repro:

  1. Go to https://docs.wasmtime.dev/cli.html
  2. Click how to enable logging
  3. Observe 404 response.
